Baxter, Hugh W. "Civil War 'Vet' Tells Vivid Story of Epic Monitor-Merrimac Battle," Baxter Family Chronicle, 1, no. 1 (April 1989): 1-3 
     _____ "John Thomas Woolsey Baxter," Baxter Family Chronicle 2, no. 3(December 1990): 2-3

O'Neil, Rear Adm. Charles, USN, Ret. "Engagement Between the Cumberland and Merrimack". United States Naval Institute Proceedings 48, no. 6 (June 1922): 863-892 
Selfridge, Read Adm. Thomas O., Jr., USN. "The Story of the Cumberland." Military Historical Society of Massachusetts, Naval Actions and History, 1799-1898 (Boston, 1902): 101-126. --></p>
