			<li><A NAME=BradfordN56></A><STRONG>Bradford</STRONG>, Ned (Editor).<BR>
				<FONT COLOR="#DC143C"><I><STRONG>Battles and Leaders of the Civil War</STRONG></I></FONT>.<BR>
				Meridian (Penguin Books USA), New York. 1989. 626pp <A HREF="../../vacsn4/original/index.htm#BrookeJM87"><img src="../../myicons/eye.gif" alt="eye" width="19" height="12" border="0"></A><A HREF="../../vacsn4/original/index.htm#WoodJT87"><img src="../../myicons/eye.gif" alt="eye" width="19" height="12" border="0"></A><A HREF="../../vacsn4/original/index.htm#ColstonRE84"><img src="../../myicons/eye.gif" alt="eye" width="19" height="12" border="0"></A><A HREF="../../vacsn4/original/index.htm#BrookeJM87"><img src="../../myicons/eye.gif" alt="eye" width="19" height="12" border="0"></A><A HREF="../../vacsn4/original/index.htm#PorterJL87"><img src="../../myicons/eye.gif" alt="eye" width="19" height="11" border="0"></A><A HREF="../../vacsn4/original/index.htm#GreeneSD84"><img src="../../myicons/eye.gif" alt="eye" width="19" height="11" border="0"></A><A HREF="../../vacsn4/original/index.htm#ButtsFB85"><img src="../../myicons/eye.gif" alt="eye" width="19" height="11" border="0"></A><A HREF="../../vacsn4/original/index.htm#ReaneyH84"><img src="../../myicons/eye.gif" alt="eye" width="19" height="11" border="0"></A><A HREF="../../vacsn4/original/index.htm#EricssonJ87"><img src="../../myicons/eye.gif" alt="eye" width="19" height="11" border="0"></A><BR>
				<FONT SIZE="-1">Originally published in 1956, this book reprints the words of the participants of the Civil War. It contains articles by Lt. Wood of the <I>Virginia</I> and Lt. Greene of the <I>Monitor</I>. This is just a subset of the works in the full Battles and Leaders of the Civil War published in 1887-1888. (see Johnson below)</FONT> <FONT SIZE="-1">(Electronic copy at  <a href="http://ehistory.osu.edu/uscw/library/books/battles/index.cfm" target="x">eHistory</a>.  Copy at MT)</FONT>
